# Smart Parking System (IoT + ESP32 + MIT App)

This project is a smart parking solution using ESP32, IR sensors, RFID authentication, and MIT App Inventor.

## 🛠️ Hardware Used
- ESP32
- 3 x IR Sensors (slot detection)
- Ultrasonic Sensor (exit detection)
- RFID Reader + Tags (entry authentication)
- SG90 Servo Motor (gate control)
- Jumper wires, breadboard, etc.

## 📱 MIT App
The app displays real-time slot availability by fetching data from ThingSpeak.

## ☁️ Cloud Platform
- ThingSpeak (for real-time data updates)

